查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-details-upcoming-single-the-giver-my-take-on-cntry-3843643?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chappell-roan-details-upcoming-single-the-giver-my-take-on-cntrySurej Singh Wed, 05 Mar 2025 01:39:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3843643 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她还澄清了她的下一张唱片是否将是乡村专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-details-upcoming-single-the-giver-my-take-on-cntry-3843643">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）的帖子详细介绍了即将发行的单曲“ The Giver”：“我对C*ntry的看法”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>透露了有关她即将发行的单曲“ The Giver”的几个关键细节 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）：流行超新星，他感觉就像是“拖拉赛”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>“好运宝贝！”歌手已经嘲笑“送礼者”已经有一段时间了， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-debuts-new-lesbian-anthem-country-song-on-snl-3809048">在去年11月的星期六夜现场露面时</a>首次表演了曲目。上个月，罗恩（Roan） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-plumber-version-of-new-single-the-giver-3841347">针对“送礼者”（The Giver）的两个变体宣布了乙烯基预订，称为“水管工版”和“律师版”</a> - 这些乙烯基订单预计将于8月发货。</p><p>现在，查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）宣布“送礼者”将于3月13日发布。她还确认，这首歌将是她与丹·尼格罗（Dan Nigro）一起写的乡村音乐。她在Instagram上写了这首歌：“我们从来没有做过乡村歌曲，我在乡村音乐中有一个特别的位置。我每天早晨和下午在我的校车上听着它，并在Bon Fires，杂货店和卡拉OK酒吧在我周围旋转。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGyk6MqRHXu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div