performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Julian-Casablancas">朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas）</a> + <a href="/artists/The-Voidz">voidz</a>从即将到来的EP中分享了他们未来派的新单曲“蓝色恶魔”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/julian-casablancas-interview-the-voidz-like-all-before-you-album-3795205">朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas）将世界设定为权利：“我们总是认为我们如此特别，超越了旧的方式，但我们不是”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该曲目以Voidz的签名合成器较重的实验节拍以及Casablancas的自动调节重型人声演唱：<br />我们互相战斗 /像两个兄弟 /父亲一样，原谅我起义 /太多的婴儿 /像母亲一样死了，”描述了一场冲突。</p><p> “蓝色恶魔”在乐队的官方Instagram帐户上被取笑，并由AI创建了几个帖子。第一个剪辑看到一位新闻记者阅读了乐队的“前社交媒体经理” Tron Cole的来信，他威胁要泄露乐队的新音乐。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="voidz-蓝色恶魔（歌词）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WEZJpFXKTPk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>根据新闻稿，该曲目是Voidz即将发行的EP的第一个品尝器，该曲目将于今年春季晚些时候发布。 “ Blue Demon”是乐队发行的第一首新音乐，其第三张和最新专辑《 2024年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-you-release-atmospheric-opener-overture-3772961#:~:text=In%20a%20four%2Dstar%20review,as%20part%20of%20The%20Strokes.">“像之前”</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，Voidz <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julian-casablancas-the-voidz-announce-2025-london-show-buy-tickets-3818774">将于明天（3月5日）在巴黎的Les Inrocks音乐节上演出，并于3月8日（3月8日）在Troxy举行的伦敦举行的一次演出</a>。这两种出现以前都被称为“两晚混乱和超越”。</p><p>它补充说：“这些即将到来的表现有望提供Voidz的标志性融合，具有无情的能量，反对流派的音景以及令人着迷的表演，这些表演已成为他们现场体验的标志。”两场音乐会都将以尚未宣布的特别嘉宾为特色。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGgDU3SOn_q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.